The Issues view is useful for mining or search for issues that many have fallen off the queue.  As an agent, this is replaced by the "Queues" but is still there for non-agent JIRA users.

 

An agent can still get to it via the topbar's "Issues" link and then clicking on a search.  However, it is more intuitive to use the current project's sidebar instead.

