As an Service Desk Administrator, I want to create queues that also enable to filter for non-service Desk projects. Basically, we are working with two major projects, one for Support and anotherone for Development.

In the past we were working with a Dashboard, among others including a filter that listed tickets from Development project, that are assigned to support for addressing questions to support. We would like to have a queue that lists those tickets again.

