h3. Summary
When restoring a lower version of JIRA Service Desk Server to Cloud, an inappropriate error message will show.

h3. Steps to reproduce
# Restore JIRA Service Desk with version 3.0 to Cloud

h3. Expected Result:
Import successfully.

